flowchart TD
  %% ============ Entrada / Orquestación ============
  A[Bitbucket Issue + comentarios / señal ADW] --> B[Runner Orquestador (Webhook Receiver)]

  %% ============ Pre-Project Hook ============
  B --> C{Pre-Project Hook}
  C -->|valida| C1[claude.md + architecture.md]
  C -->|ok| D
  C -->|fail| Z[Stop: falta contexto mínimo]

  %% ============ Contrato de método ============
  D[Spec-kit + Templates + Diagrams] --> E{Ejecutar agentes por fase}

  %% ============ Agentes (especialidades) ============
  E --> P1[Phase 1: Planning / Scheduler]
  E --> P2[Phase 2: Backend + OpenAPI/Swagger]
  E --> P3[Phase 3: Frontend UI (Web/App)]
  E --> P4[Phase 4: Integración & Calidad]
  E --> P5[Phase 5: CI/CD Deploy]

  %% ============ Pila de agentes ============
  subgraph F[Agents (rol + restricciones)]
    FAout[Outputs consolidados] 
    FA1[Architect] --> FAout
    FA2[Fullstack Developer] --> FAout
    FA3[Flutter Developer] --> FAout
    FA4[Data Engineer] --> FAout
    FA5[Fixed Errors] --> FAout
    FA6[Auditor] --> FAout

    FP1[HU Work Planner] --> FAout
    FP2[Gimena Scheduler] --> FAout

    FQA1[QA Integrator (API Testing)] --> FAout
    FI1[Integration (UI ↔ API)] --> FAout

    FQ2[Sonar Quality Gate] --> FAout
    FU1[Unit Test Standards Reviewer] --> FAout
    FMCP[MCP Integration Tester] --> FAout
    FV[Video Recorder] --> FAout
    FGR[Quality Report Generator] --> FAout
  end

  %% ============ Hooks Post-query / KPI ============
  P1 --> H{Post-Query Hook (kpi.txt)}
  P2 --> H
  P3 --> H
  P4 --> H
  P5 --> H
  H --> I[Actualiza kpi.txt (tokens + status)]

  %% ============ PR / Pipelines ============
  I --> J[Outputs + evidencias verificables]
  J --> K[PR en Bitbucket (branch + commits + revisión)]
  K --> L[Bitbucket Pipelines]

  %% ============ Deploy + Feedback ============
  L --> M[Deploy automático]
  M --> M1[Containers/API (EC2) o Apps (tiendas)]
  M1 --> N[Feedback loop: logs, crash/analytics, métricas]
  N --> A

